---
export const prerender = true;
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es-MX">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#E87200" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="default" />
    <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
    <meta name="description" content="Control total de tu flota, en la palma de tu mano" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icons/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" crossorigin />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Sin conexión - FleetFuel</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-bg text-text min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 dot-pattern">
    <div class="w-full max-w-sm text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-surface border border-border mb-6">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth={1.5}>
          <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" d="M18.364 5.636a9 9 0 11-12.728 12.728M5.636 18.364a9 9 0 0112.728-12.728" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-text mb-2">Sin conexión</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">
        No hay acceso a Internet. Los registros se guardarán localmente y se sincronizarán automáticamente cuando vuelvas a estar en línea.
      </p>
      <button
        onclick="window.location.reload()"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 h-12 px-6 bg-accent hover:bg-accent/90 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors mx-auto"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth={2.5}>
          <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
        </svg>
        Reintentar
      </button>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
